title: Install Prettier Into a React Project
tags: @zettel _method
roam-id: 7ca3a851-3126-4ff0-995d-8fd4da770808
type: text/markdown

- under your project root create `.prettierrc` file

- put the following into it

  ``` json
  {
    "tabWidth": 2,
    "semi": true,
    "singleQuote": true,
    "trailingComma": "all"
  }
  ```

- install prettier

  ``` bash
  npm install --save-dev --save-exact prettier
  ```
